The paper also discusses the use of suffix-trees, which are commonly used in data structures and algorithms, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses the use of feature-based classifiers, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the storage of long training sequences, which is a common topic in databases (cs.DB).
